## Watch result

The watch queried `agent_triggers` and `messages` for about 110 seconds after
the trigger was observed.

```text
trigger.claimed_at: null
trigger.completed_at: null
maya_ack: null
last_observation_elapsed_ms: 110471
```

No matching local log lines appeared for:

```text
T5D_DIRECT_QUEUE_PROBE_20260522T222533Z
59D84468-A2F0-453C-B43B-6FF7DE1E459D
executeAgentTurn START for Maya after 2026-05-22T22:25:33Z
